title: Unemployment rate in Brunei Darussalam 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Unemployment rate, containing a total of 21 data points.
Overall Unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Unemployment rate, of value 9.32 was reached at Year 2017
Minimum Unemployment rate about 5.57 was reached at Year 1999
